comments: well, that match was close. Takes way too long to get gears
Somehow this robot has taken like 15 consecutive Ls, yet is still ranked higher than us.
They played a lot of defense, not good for much else though
it hung really fast, but had a lot of trouble getting gears
It tried to shoot i think, but overall was low key carried and easily pushed around
TBH was surprised it hung, this thing is MASSIVE
once it got the rope it moved up pretty quickly
pretty fast and does well collecting and getting the team gears.. also can climb well
slow with climbing, if they had got the rope any later they wouldn't of made it
stopped moving like 30 seconds in  but ended up going again after a while and then stopped moving again with like 30 seconds left.
it was pretty close to not making the hang and holding its own weight
